des: Coming to you from the birthplace of Southern Rock, it's all about the music. Florida has been home to many influential musicians across various genres. The perfect launching pad for Sonic Planet. Hear a mix of the roots: rock, folk, soul and funk from a diversity of artists. New and established Florida artists are invited to share their music.
